{"tid":2345426,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[英軍服務團] 化學師雷福榮一躍而下死亡，寧死不篤灰","createTime":"2020-12-29T12:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T08:28:04.000Z","uid":43150,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"db0904d801cce25469367b1f664a7241f5af22cf","tid":2345426,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T12:57:21.000Z","msg":"雷福榮 David Loie，生於紐西蘭，出生年份不詳，後受聘於香港政府做化驗師同後備警察。<br />\n<br />\n1941年聖誕節香港淪陷之後雷福榮繼續佢嘅工作，並暗中同英軍服務團(British Army Aid Group) 聯絡。BAAG 聯絡到英軍戰俘，準備策劃佢地逃走。雷福榮當時係M組首領。可惜1943年，風聲走漏，俾日軍知道咗。<br />\n日軍大肆搜捕有關人等，拉咗雷福榮，劉德愛（雷嘅太太），防衛司Fraser，Ansari上尉等等。佢，Fraser，Ansari 等等都拒絕篤灰，最後押雷福榮的法十個時，佢被押去法庭個陣掙脫日軍跳樓自殺，而太太劉德愛等人被日軍處死。<br />\n<br />\n//日軍反間諜行動<br />\n1943年春，日本憲兵隊展開行動，打擊地下抵抗活動。是年3月，位於沙頭角的中共據點遭到突襲，而國軍特務人員的秘密基地亦遭破獲。<br />\n<br />\n日軍亦曾以運送金錢到赤柱拘留營為名，拘捕司徒永覺醫生；及後又因此案拘捕數名銀行家及醫護人員。日軍懷疑司徒永覺是英軍在港情報系統的首領；被捕者還包括匯豐銀行大班祈禮賓，他最終因為遭受酷刑及營養不良，在赤柱監獄離世。<br />\n<br />\n匯豐銀行大班祈禮賓<br />\n1943年4月，日本憲兵隊又成功滲透英軍服務團及戰俘營之間的聯繫網絡。是時，印度獨立聯盟成員冒充印軍軍官安沙里上尉，誘使英軍服務團情報人員暴露身份，並使安沙里因此被捕。砵蘭街的Z站亦被日軍破獲。同年5月，「C組」有成員背叛，數名人員被捕，當中包括一名貨車司機，他一直負責為戰俘送遞訊息。<br />\n<br />\n7月1日，日軍又逼令一名和英軍服務團合作的司機在亞皆老街戰俘營向戰俘傳遞假訊息。日軍計謀得逞以後，亞皆老街及深水埗戰俘營內官兵數人被捕。7月10日，紐臨上校被捕。<br />\n<br />\n同日被日本憲兵隊拘捕者，還包括霍德上尉、皇家空軍的加利中尉，以及身處深水埗戰俘營的皇家加拿大通訊軍團萊歷治中士。至此，戰俘營地下抵抗活動的中堅份子大多被捕。<br />\n<br />\n日軍亦破獲了英軍服務團的情報網。1943年4月，日軍登上在澳門的西安號輪船，在船上發現文件，記載了英軍服務團其中一個情報組的資料。日軍由此得知英軍服<strong>務團在香港擁有情報網。憲兵隊旋即在市內搜捕英軍服務團人員，並在5月31日拘捕「M組」首領雷福榮；他隨即自殺，以免被迫供出他人。<br />\n<br />\n結果，華洋軍民被捕者超過二百人，其中約四十人遭處決，包括紐臨、霍德，以及加利，英軍服務團情報人員包括George Kotewall、劉德愛（雷福榮伴侶）、劉德光（劉德愛兄弟）、李林（戰俘營司機）、曾德、曾耀生兄弟（情報員，其父曾協助與啟德機場的戰俘聯絡）、楊守德（自日本海軍工作部竊取圖則）等。其餘被捕者則遭受酷刑及囚禁，直至日本投降為止。莫德庇少將曾要求日軍釋放他的官兵，但最終與其他高級戰俘被送到台灣囚禁。</strong>//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.arcgis.com/apps/Cascade/index.html?appid=271ca27a3bdb4fed8c7381953ab7d146\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arcgis.com%2Fapps%2FCascade%2Findex.html%3Fappid%3D271ca27a3bdb4fed8c7381953ab7d146&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGbuZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=cf0a2790\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.arcgis.com/apps/Cascade/index.html?appid=271ca27a3bdb4fed8c7381953ab7d146</a><br />\n<br />\n另見<br />\n<a href=\"https://gwulo.com/node/19439\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgwulo.com%2Fnode%2F19439&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGbuZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=17b75617\" target=\"_blank\">https://gwulo.com/node/19439</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://matters.news/@movistoryhk/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%85%E9%A0%88%E8%A6%81%E7%9F%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF-%E6%88%B0%E4%BF%98%E7%87%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%B5%E6%8A%97%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95-%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4%E9%9B%B6%E5%85%AB%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%88%B0%E4%BF%98%E7%87%9F-%E8%8B%B1%E8%BB%8D%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E5%9C%98-%E7%AD%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89-bafyreigrjsonrngmx3wi6r4g7tl5k3dmtvvsdpszq3zryyb6u4steqivam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmatters.news%2F%40movistoryhk%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25BF%2585%25E9%25A0%2588%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%259F%25A5%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2585%2589%25E4%25B9%258B%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E6%2588%25B0%25E4%25BF%2598%25E7%2587%259F%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%258A%25B5%25E6%258A%2597%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%259B%25B6%25E5%2585%25AB%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2588%25B0%25E4%25BF%2598%25E7%2587%259F-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%259C%2598-%25E7%25AD%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2585%2589-bafyreigrjsonrngmx3wi6r4g7tl5k3dmtvvsdpszq3zryyb6u4steqivam&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGbuZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=45e3ac86\" target=\"_blank\">https://matters.news/@movistoryhk/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%85%E9%A0%88%E8%A6%81%E7%9F%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF-%E6%88%B0%E4%BF%98%E7%87%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%B5%E6%8A%97%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95-%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4%E9%9B%B6%E5%85%AB%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%88%B0%E4%BF%98%E7%87%9F-%E8%8B%B1%E8%BB%8D%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E5%9C%98-%E7%AD%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89-bafyreigrjsonrngmx3wi6r4g7tl5k3dmtvvsdpszq3zryyb6u4steqivam</a>"},{"pid":"d7eeba25eb55ddab1ffdf89f05a32e839242fbf1","tid":2345426,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0546d38ec70cb7dbdfa4b4efec4b24f84c56d6","tid":2345426,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:21:47.000Z","msg":"英雄"},{"pid":"c6a2bb69cba0290c6ee6f89682c64a324d5d2e6e","tid":2345426,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538c0ff22d3e400bad0d801614fc84d0b5801477","tid":2345426,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b030ba6358427b477c664d9212aa8a68c25f32d6","tid":2345426,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee81430adee4dd7b4111f4e69abe56d6be003315","tid":2345426,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd457a441fcab445af60eac4181a490e57de2263","tid":2345426,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:54:32.000Z","msg":"今時今日都係咁<br />\n一有圈子成形，區議會，黃圈<br />\n共狗不斷滲透，分化"},{"pid":"0231e32d0d52aae19ed60bddaa7b6b4109d9e6f0","tid":2345426,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T14:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反姓劉個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce7af6fe2b8d51169aac45202893da566b136ce","tid":2345426,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd457a441fcab445af60eac4181a490e57de2263","tid":2345426,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:54:32.000Z","msg":"今時今日都係咁<br />\n一有圈子成形，區議會，黃圈<br />\n共狗不斷滲透，分化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T15:43:03.000Z","msg":"有啲係印度人，可能想借日本幫手趕走英國<br />\n又或者有啲英國人轉向日本效忠<br />\n當然香港人都有，去做憲查幫手周街打人"},{"pid":"7ba862333d6b67a385240dc27ab394af8bf1246f","tid":2345426,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:20:43.000Z","msg":"BAAG仲有其他成員，包括：<br />\n-<strong>Thomas Tim WONG (aka WONG Wang Tim) </strong><br />\n佢都係後備警察，香港投降之前已經俾日軍捉咗。不過個晚已經走甩咗，之後加入BAAG M組。負責文宣。<br />\n//After the surrender of Hongkong, I began to discuss with the late Mr David Loie and Mr C C Mok to form an espionage group from former members of the Police Reserves ... to continue  the prosecution of the war underground.  [The BAAG] decision to support our movement later brought the &quot;M&quot; group into existence.  ...  Upon discovery by the Japanese of my activities, I escaped to Waichow, and posted to take charge of news propaganda work at BAAG AHQ.  //<br />\n<a href=\"https://gwulo.com/node/24628\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgwulo.com%2Fnode%2F24628&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGbuZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=3db0b7c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://gwulo.com/node/24628</a><br />\n<strong>-Chi-ping / Maximo Cheng (鄭治平)</strong> (01/01/1921-01/01/2014) <br />\n香港保衛戰爆發時為防衛軍成員。香港投降後去咗桂林加入BAaAG。之後成為Chindits一份子，出征緬甸。<br />\n<a href=\"https://gwulo.com/node/19737\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgwulo.com%2Fnode%2F19737&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGbuZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=a650c715\" target=\"_blank\">https://gwulo.com/node/19737</a>"},{"pid":"d5eca9a7a5937a6a4acf62b509810f5801fff60d","tid":2345426,"uid":43150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:28:04.000Z","msg":"多謝Gwulo收集整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有大量BAAG成員，當中包括賴廉士助手，花名李雞嘅李耀標，65號徐家祥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，片有雷福榮嘅太太劉德愛女士等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gwulo.com/node/27231\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgwulo.com%2Fnode%2F27231&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGbuZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=b3722ae6\" target=\"_blank\">https://gwulo.com/node/27231</a>"}]}